the 13th movies, but he also started Hollywood Ghost Hunters.  

I&#39;m always looking for people to test the boxes out for me.  I&#39;ve  given 
them to Steve Gonsalves and Dave Tango from ghost hunters, Chris Fleming  from 
psychic kids, Zak Bagans from Ghost adventures, Robb Demerest from Ghost  
hunters International, Kane Hodder, Bill Murphy, Frank Sumption, April 
Slaughter  and Chris Moon.

I figured that if i can&#39;t be a celebrity, maybe my box will.

-Steve H.



